<h2>OPPORTUNITY TYPES</h2>
<div class='c'><div class='h' style='background:#E3F2FD'><div class='d' style='background:#1E88E5'></div>FW - Both Depth/Stack</div><div class='b'>Can add cases front-to-back AND stack higher. Highest impact.<br><span class='f'>CASES_PER_LANE > CASECAP AND MAX_STACK >= 2</span></div></div>
<div class='c'><div class='h' style='background:#E8F5E9'><div class='d' style='background:#4CAF50'></div>FW - DoubleStack</div><div class='b'>Can stack higher but depth is maximized.<br><span class='f'>MAX_STACK_LAYERS >= 2</span></div></div>
